Package com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.dispatching

Class GenericEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dv8tion.jda.api.events.Event
      • com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.dispatching.GenericEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.dv8tion.jda.api.events.GenericEvent
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ButtonEvent, CommandEvent
    public class GenericEvent
extends net.dv8tion.jda.api.events.Event
    Extension of JDAs Event class that combines all common fields of all interaction events. This is the base class for the different event classes.
    Since:
    4.0.0
    Version:
    4.0.0
    Author:
    Kaktushose
    See Also:
    CommandEvent, ButtonEvent
